<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>注册</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://cdn.static.runoob.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="http://cdn.static.runoob.com/libs/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/login.css">
    <script src="../js/login.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <a class="backhome" href="index"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-menu-left">返回首页</i></a>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-3 reg">
            <label>有朋自远方来，不亦乐乎？欢迎加入友家！</label>
            <form>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">帐户:</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="username" id="regname" placeholder="请输入帐户">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="pwd">密码:</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" name="passwd" id="regpwd" placeholder="请输入密码">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="pwd1">密码:</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" name="passwd1" id="regpwd1" placeholder="请重复输入密码">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="tel">手机号:</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="usertel" id="regtel" placeholder="请输入手机号">
                </div>
                <button id="btn-reg" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">注册</button>
                <button id="btn-tologin" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">登录</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>